Q: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/10183-total-cost-of-orders?code_type=5

Sol: 

select
    c.id,
    c.first_name,
    sum (o.total_order_cost) as total_order_cost
from customers as c
    inner join orders as o
        on c.id = o.cust_id
group by c.id, c.first_name
order by c.first_name asc;
